text: Nantucket Memorial Airport (airport code KACK) serves the city of Nantucket, Massachusetts. The airport opened in 2009. The following airlines fly to Nantucket Memorial Airport: *Cape Air (Hub) *Delta Connection (sometimes) *Island Airlines *JetBlue Airways (sometimes) *Nantucket Airlines *Ultimate Air Shuttle *United Express (sometimes) *US Airways (sometimes) ==References== Category:Airports in the United States Category:Transport in Massachusetts Category:Buildings and structures in Massachusetts Category:2009 establishments in the United States Category:2000s establishments in Massachusetts
title: Nantucket Memorial Airport
